message: Fixed The grammar and English writing basically- it was obviously written by a source who's first language was not English.
Added detail and a martyr regarded as the shield of India.
Fixed an inaccurate statement, the Sikh rebels attacked the rulers because they were oppressive, they did not attack innocent civilians.

/* Some historic famous martyrs */ Everyone on that list deserves to be there. If one wants to, one should add more so everyone can know about heroic martyrs. Don't take any of these heroes off though?
I have put the list back to it's original form before someone allegedly took away all the famous martyrs of the Sikh religion out of the list.
